{"tid":1726644,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"開始有人推，全民要有架生，保護自己同身邊人！","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:41:38.000Z","uid":265101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6b8698b262aa2da76afb10759657d77c624e4a","tid":1726644,"uid":265101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"開始有人推，全民要有架生，保護自己同身邊人！<br />\n<br />\n反思上水女手足比人捉住，無架生真係唔太敢埋去救<br />\n仲有大埔劏肚果個男仔，根本唔應該比個兇手大陸仔行得走得，自發神心先走去自首；如果佢唔係走去自首，而係在襲擊其他人，咪變左社會上計時炸彈！？<br />\n<br />\n香港人反抗！ 唔可以只係口號！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8BBEmH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8BBEmH.jpg&h=b065e908&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"607312a8da0df9fbc79cba348c195a6632329d95","tid":1726644,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:41:10.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" da